This repository includes code derived from the following projects:

1. COIN-LIO (https://github.com/ethz-asl/COIN-LIO)
   Copyright (c) 2024, Autonomous Systems Lab, ETH Zurich
   License: BSD 3-Clause (above) for new COIN-LIO code,
            GNU GPL v2 for code derived from FAST-LIO2.
   See src/coin_lio/LICENSE for the full dual-license text.

   Included in: src/coin_lio/
   Modifications: ROS 1 → ROS 2 Humble port, Ouster metadata parameter
                  loading, FIR filter integration, LiDAR callback throttling,
                  debug output cleanup, Dense RGB-D mapper integration.

2. FAST-LIO2 (https://github.com/hku-mars/FAST_LIO)
   Copyright (c) 2021, HKU-MARS Lab
   License: GNU GPL v2
   Used as the base ESIKF/ikd-Tree framework inside src/coin_lio/src/laserMapping.cpp.
   See src/coin_lio/LICENSE for the full GPL v2 text.

3. LOAM (Zhang & Singh, CMU)
   Copyright 2013, Ji Zhang, Carnegie Mellon University
   Used as historical reference in src/coin_lio/src/laserMapping.cpp header.

Other packages in this repository (vill_slam, vill_slam_msgs,
vill_slam_recorder, vill_slam_ui, line_laser_driver) are original work
released under the BSD 3-Clause license above.

Note on license compatibility: because src/coin_lio/ incorporates GPL v2
code (from FAST-LIO2), any redistribution of that directory is subject to
GPL v2 terms. The rest of this repository, which does not link against
src/coin_lio/ as a library, remains under BSD 3-Clause. Users combining
src/coin_lio/ with other components in binary form should comply with
GPL v2 requirements for that combination.
